name: in the village of Polyanivka
column4: they "asked" residents to move to other settlements. Concrete slabs removed from the water channel were brought to Polyanivka via nearby Yakymivka. And they turn the surrounding area into an outpost.

WKT: There is information that the orcs are sitting in empty houses with. Krymskoye
name: they appointed a local forester
description: he and his wife guard the forest so that no one from the locals goes there.

name: the Wagnerites are stationed there
description: perhaps they are hiding something in the forest.
